OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,FA postman killed his son by shaking
OL,7,Fhim violently after returning from a
OL,8,Fnight out, a jury heard.
OL,10,FTony Bartlett, 39, denies charges of
OL,11,Fmurder and manslaughter relating to
OL,12,Fthe death of Atticus Bartlett.
OL,14,FAtticus was four weeks old when he
OL,15,Fcollapsed at his home in Chard,
OL,16,FSomerset, at about 11pm on 16 July,
OL,17,F2022.
OL,19,FHe was taken to hospital in a critical
OL,20,Fcondition but never regained
OL,21,Fconsciousness and died on 23 July.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
