OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,FProsecuting, Charles Row KC told the
OL,7,Fjury of six men and six women that
OL,8,FAtticus had previously been "fit and
OL,9,Fhealthy".
OL,11,FThe baby boy had been cared for by his
OL,12,Fgrandparents while his parents,
OL,13,FBartlett and his partner Evelyn
OL,14,FBallentyne, went out for the evening.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
