OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,F"It is the Crown's case that, having
OL,7,Fbeen on a night out and having
OL,8,Fconsumed up to nine pints of beer,
OL,9,FTony Bartlett was left to look after
OL,10,Fand feed Atticus for just a few
OL,11,Fmoments while Evelyn went upstairs to
OL,12,Fchange and get ready for bed," Mr Row
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"In those few moments, Tony Bartlett
OL,16,Fviolently shook his child so hard that
OL,17,Fhe caused severe internal injuries to
OL,18,FAtticus' brain and he damaged his
OL,19,Fspinal cord.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@^O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
