PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,F"In doing so, he must have squeezed
OL,7,Fhis child so hard that he cracked
OL,8,Fseveral ribs."
OL,10,FMr Row described how Ms Ballentyne
OL,11,Fcame downstairs to hear her baby's
OL,12,F"last gasps".
OL,14,F"At that point, Atticus was lifeless,
OL,15,Fface down and across his father's
OL,16,Fknees," Mr Row said.
OL,18,FThe court heard neighbours and
OL,19,Fparamedics attended the property, with
OL,20,FAtticus taken to hospital by ambulance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NO]tD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
