PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,F"The damage to Atticus' brain was so
OL,7,Fsevere that nothing could be done," Mr
OL,8,FRow told the jury.
OL,10,F"He never managed to breathe for
OL,11,Fhimself again and he never regained
OL,12,Fconsciousness.
OL,14,F"Tragically, he died just before
OL,15,Fmidnight on 23 July 2022."
OL,17,FMr Row told the jury that "something"
OL,18,Fthat night had caused Bartlett to
OL,19,Fbecome "frustrated" with his young son.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]rD@AOUvD@AOUwD@ZO]yD@[OUyD@
OL,26,AeO]{D@HOU{D@SO]
