PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,FHe said the baby was a "difficult and
OL,7,Fmessy feeder" with a tendency to spit
OL,8,Fout his milk.
OL,10,FThat evening, Atticus had been
OL,11,F"grizzly and crying" on and off.
OL,13,FMr Row said: "Whatever happened, Tony
OL,14,FBartlett could not and did not
OL,15,Ftolerate it.
OL,17,F"It is the Crown's case that, in that
OL,18,Fmoment, Tony Bartlett shook Atticus so
OL,19,Fhard that he must have intended to
OL,20,Fcause him really serious bodily harm.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@MO]sD@AOUsD@TO]uD@NOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
