PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,F"If you shake a four-week-old baby
OL,7,Fwith so much force that you break ribs
OL,8,Fand destroy his brain, what other
OL,9,Fintention is there?"
OL,11,FThe court heard that on the night of
OL,12,F16 July, Ms Ballentyne's mother and
OL,13,Fher partner had come to babysit
OL,14,FAtticus so his parents could go out
OL,15,Ffor the first time since his birth.
OL,17,FThey arrived at the family home at
OL,18,Fabout 6pm, with Bartlett and Ms
OL,19,FBallentyne then heading to The Cerdic
OL,20,Fpub for food and drinks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
