PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,FThe couple then attended a comedy
OL,7,Fnight at Chard Guildhall, returning to
OL,8,Ftheir home at about 10.45pm.
OL,10,FAfter Ms Ballentyne's mother and her
OL,11,Fpartner left, Ms Ballentyne went
OL,12,Fupstairs to get changed.
OL,14,F"When Ms Ballentyne came back into the
OL,15,Fliving room, she saw Atticus lying
OL,16,Fface down on Mr Bartlett's lap," Mr
OL,17,FRow said.
OL,19,F"Mr Bartlett's eyes were closed. She
OL,20,Fcould tell something was seriously
OL,21,Fwrong.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@`O]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
