CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,F"As she walked in, Atticus made a
OL,7,Fcouple of strange gasping sounds. She
OL,8,Fimmediately shouted 'he's dead'."
OL,10,FBartlett, who was working as a postman
OL,11,Fat the time, allegedly moved Atticus
OL,12,Fonto his back ` with the baby "floppy
OL,13,Fand lifeless".
OL,15,FMr Row said it was unclear whether Ms
OL,16,FBallentyne had taken Atticus and tried
OL,17,Fto revive him with "gentle shaking".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]tD@_OUuD@MO]yD@TOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
