PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,FThe possibility this could have caused
OL,7,Fhis fatal injuries has been
OL,8,F"considered carefully by experts and
OL,9,Fruled out", he added.
OL,11,FParamedics arrived at the family home
OL,12,Fat 11.29pm, with Atticus taken to
OL,13,FMusgrove Park Hospital by ambulance,
OL,14,Farriving there at 12.16am.
OL,16,FHe was transferred to Bristol Royal
OL,17,FHospital for Children at 5am on 17
OL,18,FJuly.
OL,20,FHe died there on 23 July.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@JO]
