OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781385841
OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,FIn police interviews, Bartlett said he
OL,7,Fhad been feeding Atticus when the baby
OL,8,Fstarted coughing and choking.
OL,10,FThe postman told officers he was
OL,11,Frubbing and patting his son before he
OL,12,F"decided to put him on my knee and
OL,13,Fshake him a little bit on my knee".
OL,15,FHowever, he now says this is not the
OL,16,Fcase and any non-accidental injury
OL,17,Fmust have been caused by Ms
OL,18,FBallentyne, Mr Row told jurors.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
