OL,3,CPostman murdered his four-week-old son
OL,4,Cby shaking him, jury told
OL,6,F"It is his case that he bears no
OL,7,Fresponsibility for Atticus' death
OL,8,Fwhatsoever," he added.
OL,10,FBartlett, of Axminster, Devon, denies
OL,11,Fthe two charges against him and the
OL,12,Ftrial continues.
